name: INSPIRE_Q_Nelson_Industrial_Modern_Metal_Dining_Table
reviews: This table is absolutely perfect in my small dining area. The colors are beautiful, and the top is much nicer quality than I expected.
Looks just like the picture online. One leg was bent but we were still able to assemble it. The top is quite textured. The edges have a burnt finish.
Sturdy and easy to assemble but buyers should be aware top is plastic. Not a good value
I ordered this for a desk for my home office. Haven't been using it long. So far its been great!
description: This fun and functional table, at 93 pounds and measuring 30 inches tall by 72 inches wide by 36 inches deep, providing ample space for your family dining experience.
